                <li>Ensure safety and comfort in every mile you fly.</li>
                <li>Embrace innovation to provide seamless travel experiences.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="why-choose-us">
            <h2>Why Choose Smile Airlines?</h2>
